# - resource -------------------------------------------------------------------

<http://fhir.org/guides/who/emcare/CodeSystem/emc-custom-codes-codes> a fhir:CodeSystem;
  fhir:nodeRole fhir:treeRoot;
  fhir:Resource.id [ fhir:value "emc-custom-codes-codes"];
  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ];
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This code system https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/CodeSystem/emc-custom-codes-codes defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Unique identification</td><td>Unique identifier provided or a universal ID, if used in the country</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Unique identification</td><td>Auto-generated unique identification if used by the implementation</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Child's Identity unknown/prefer to remain anonymous</td><td>The client's identity is unknown or the client's prefers to remain anonymous</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE04<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE04\"> </a></td><td>First name</td><td>Client's first name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Middle Name</td><td>Client's middle name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Last name</td><td>Client's family name or last name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Date of birth</td><td>The client's date of birth (DOB), if known, OR the estimated date of birth IF not known (see EmCare.A.DE10)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Time of Birth</td><td>The client's time of birth (if &lt;1 day old)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE10<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE10\"> </a></td><td>Age</td><td>Age auto-calculated (presented as number of years, months, days) of the client based on date of birth OR estimated age OR based on auto-calculation from estimaged date of birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE11<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE11\"> </a></td><td>Date of Birth not known</td><td>The client and/or Caregiver does not know the date of birth of the client (this is to check whether the age and date of birth are facts or estimations)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE12<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE12\"> </a></td><td>Provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth</td><td>The client/caregiver will provide an estimated age or estimated date of birth</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE14.1<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE14.461\"> </a></td><td>Only know age in weeks/days/hours</td><td>The Caregiver provides the age in weeks/days/hours</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE13.1<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE13.461\"> </a></td><td>Estimated Age</td><td>The age of the client is estimated based on information provided by the caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE15.1<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE15.461\"> </a></td><td>Estimated Date of Birth</td><td>Estimated Date of Birth of the Client</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE16<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE16\"> </a></td><td>Sex</td><td>The Sex of the client</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE20<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE20\"> </a></td><td>Address</td><td>Client's home address or address that the client is consenting to disclose</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE47<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE47\"> </a></td><td>Caregiver</td><td>the child could have been created from the mother therefore a relatedpersom may already exist</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">newCaregiver<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-newCaregiver\"> </a></td><td>Register a new caregiver</td><td>nan</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE21<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE21\"> </a></td><td>Primary Caregiver First Name</td><td>The client's primary Caregiver's first name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE22<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE22\"> </a></td><td>Primary Caregiver Middle Name</td><td>The client's primary Caregiver's middle name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE23<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE23\"> </a></td><td>Primary Caregiver Last Name</td><td>The client's primary Caregiver's last name</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE35<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE35\"> </a></td><td>Caregiver's Mobile telephone number</td><td>Client's Caregiver's mobile telephone number</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE36<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE36\"> </a></td><td>Caregiver's Home telephone number</td><td>Client's Caregiver's home telephone number</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE37<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE37\"> </a></td><td>Caregiver's Work telephone number</td><td>Client's Caregiver's work telephone number</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE38<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE38\"> </a></td><td>Caregiver wants to receive SMS or other messages regarding the child's visits and health status</td><td>The caregiver wants to receive SMS or other messages regarding the client's contacts/visits and health status</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE46<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE46\"> </a></td><td>CommunicationRequest recipient</td><td>This is needed to link the CommunicationRequest to the Caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE24<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE24\"> </a></td><td>Primary Caregiver's Relationship to Client</td><td>The relationship of the primary Caregiver to the client</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE31<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE31\"> </a></td><td>Biological Mother Vital Status</td><td>The client's mother and father's vital status</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE32<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE32\"> </a></td><td>Biological Father Vital Status</td><td>The client's mother and father's vital status</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE07<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE07\"> </a></td><td>Visit date</td><td>The date and time of the client's visit</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE39<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE39\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today is the primary Caregiver</td><td>The client is at the visit with the primary Caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE45<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE45\"> </a></td><td>Participant type Person accompanying child</td><td>Participant type Person accompanying child</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE44<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE44\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today</td><td>Person accompanying child today</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE40<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE40\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today's First Name</td><td>First name of person accompanying child today when client has not arrived with the primary Caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE41<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE41\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today's Last Name</td><td>Last name of person accompanying child today when client has not arrived with the primary Caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE42<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE42\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today's contact's phone number</td><td>Phone number of the visit Caregiver</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.A.DE43<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46A.46DE43\"> </a></td><td>Person accompanying child today's Relationship to Client</td><td>The relationship of the visit Caregiver to the client</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B2.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B2.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Type of Visit</td><td>This is the type of visit - planned or unplanned</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B3.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B3.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Reason for Consultation</td><td>The reason for the client's consultation</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B3.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B3.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Is the child sick today?</td><td>The client's visit is for a well child but the child is also presenting as sick</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B3.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B3.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Type of Consultation</td><td>The client's visit is for a new consultation</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B3.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B3.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Referred by a Health Care Worker or Health Care Facility</td><td>The client was referred by a Health Care Worker in the community or another Health Care Facility</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Auxiliary Temperature</td><td>The client's axillary temperature in degrees Celsius (temperature taken under the armpit)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Prefer to take Rectal Temperature</td><td>The health care worker prefers to take the client's rectal temperature</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Rectal Temperature</td><td>The client's rectal temperature in degrees Celsius (temperature taken in the rectum)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE04<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE04\"> </a></td><td>Thermometer not available</td><td>A thermometer is not available to accurately measure the client's temperature</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Hot to Touch</td><td>The client is hot to touch</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Weight</td><td>The client's weight in Kilograms</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE07<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE07\"> </a></td><td>Weight cannot be measured</td><td>The client's weight cannot be measured</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Estimated Weight</td><td>The client's weight has been estimated - to be used for treatment dosing only</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Height</td><td>The client's height in Centimeters</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE10<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE10\"> </a></td><td>Prefer to measure length</td><td>The health care worker would prefer to measure the client using length</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE11<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE11\"> </a></td><td>Height cannot be measured</td><td>The client's height cannot be measured</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE12<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE12\"> </a></td><td>Length</td><td>The client's length in Centimeters</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE13<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE13\"> </a></td><td>Length cannot be measured</td><td>The client's length cannot be measured</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE14<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE14\"> </a></td><td>Weight for Height (WFH) Z Scores</td><td>The client's weight for height Z Score</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE15<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE15\"> </a></td><td>Weight for Length (WFL) Z Scores</td><td>The client's weight for length Z Score</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE16<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE16\"> </a></td><td>Weight for Age (WFA) Z Scores</td><td>The client's weight for age z score</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE17<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE17\"> </a></td><td>MUAC (Mid Upper Arm Circumference)</td><td>The client's Mid Upper Arm Circumference in Millimeters (child ≥6 months old)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE18<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE18\"> </a></td><td>Visually assess for whether underweight (for drug dose calculation)</td><td>The health care worker visually assesses for whether underweight (for drug dosing calculations)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B6.DE22<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B6.46DE22\"> </a></td><td>Date of measurement</td><td>The date when the measurement was taken</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Obstructed or Absent Breathing</td><td>The client has obstructed or absent breathing</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Convulsing Now</td><td>The client is convulsing now</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Convulsion(s) in this Illness</td><td>The client is reported to have had one or more convulsions</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE04<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE04\"> </a></td><td>Number of convulsions in this illness</td><td>The number of convulsion(s) the client is reported to have had in this illness</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Unconscious or Lethargic</td><td>The client is unconscious or lethargic</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE09<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE09\"> </a></td><td>Not able to drink or breastfeed</td><td>The client has reported not to have been able to drink or breastfeed or currently is not able to drink or breastfeed.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE10<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE10\"> </a></td><td>Vomiting</td><td>The client is reported to be vomiting everything or vomiting but not everything or no vomiting</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B7.DE14<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B7.46DE14\"> </a></td><td>Oral Fluid Test</td><td>The healthcare worker or care giver  offers the client fluid to check if the client can drink and to check reactions (oral fluid test)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B8/B9.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B8.47B9.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Obstructed or Absent Breathing</td><td>The client has obstructed or absent breathing</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B8/B9.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B8.47B9.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Convulsing Now</td><td>The client is convulsing now</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B10S1.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B10S1.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Cough</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had a cough</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B10S1.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B10S1.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Cough for how long?</td><td>Length of time the client is reported to have or has had the cough</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B10S1.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B10S1.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Difficulty Breathing</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had difficulty breathing</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B10S1.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B10S1.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Difficulty breathing for how long?</td><td>The length of time the client has or has had difficulty breathing</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B11S1.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B11S1.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Diarrhoea</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had diarrhoea</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B11S1.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B11S1.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Diarrhoea for how long?</td><td>The length of time the client is reported to have or has had diarrhoea</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B11S1.DE05<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B11S1.46DE05\"> </a></td><td>Blood in the stool in this Illness</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had blood in the stool in this Illness</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Fever</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had fever</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Fever for how long?</td><td>The length of time the client has or has had fever</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE06<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE06\"> </a></td><td>Has Fever been present every day since the Fever started?</td><td>The client has had fever present every day since the fever started</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE07<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE07\"> </a></td><td>Refusal to Use a Limb</td><td>The client is reported to be refusing to use a limb</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE08<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE08\"> </a></td><td>Pain</td><td>The client is reported to have,  has had, or appears to be in pain</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE13<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE13\"> </a></td><td>Malaria Risk</td><td>The client is in a high / low / no malaria risk area</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B12S1.DE17<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B12S1.46DE17\"> </a></td><td>Recent Travel to a High Malaria Risk area</td><td>The client has recently travelled to a high Malaria risk area</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B13S1.DE01<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B13S1.46DE01\"> </a></td><td>Ear problem</td><td>The client is reported to have had or has an ear problem</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B13S1.DE02<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B13S1.46DE02\"> </a></td><td>Ear pain</td><td>The client is reported to have had or has ear pain</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EmCare.B13S1.DE03<a name=\"emc-custom-codes-codes-EmCare.46B13S1.46DE03\"> </a></td><td>Ear discharge</td><td>The client is reported to have or has had ear discharge</td></tr><tr><